Package: avpMap
Type: Package
Title: avpMap: Build visualizations for the Arizona Voter Project
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Christopher Weber
Maintainer: Christopher Weber <christopher.weber9874@gmail.com>
Description: The Arizona Voter Project (AVP) is a project to build a comprehensive database of voter registration and election data for the state of Arizona. The project is supported by the University of Arizona. This package provides functions to build visualizations of the data collected by the AVP.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
